data.description: Beautiful and spacious 3 bed 2 bath home w/ 2 car garage, plus an extra garage/shop on 1.26 acres. Landscaped front and back, covered patio, storage building, chicken coop, fenced yard and back fenced for horses or other animals. Small community has shared well, mailboxes and trash collection for $50 per month with no HOA rules. Near Pinal County Fairgrounds and Eleven Mile Corner. Easy access to I-10 and I-8. Perfect for your place in the country, yet close to Casa Grande and Coolidge. Buyer to verify all pertinent information.
